title: Best of the Big Bands (Big Papi) Historical Jazz Collection
description:
Source:  CD + Fresh Cover Art Scan

If you love old jazz and band music that transports you to that time then this is the compilation for you.  These are conversions from old tapes and records and some tracks do contain artifacts from that time.  

If you care more about dynamic range, 21.5Hz and wow flutter then please just keep moving along and let those who love music enjoy this for what it is.

- Big Papi
